  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM12">
<l>tollai viṉaivantu cūḻāmuṉ tāḻāmē</l>
<l>yollai vaṇaṅki yumaiyeṉṉu - melliyalōr</l>
<l>kūṟṟāṉaik kūṟṟuruvaṅ kāyntāṉai vāyntilaṅku</l>
<l>nīṟṟāṉai neñcē niṉai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before [your] old deeds come [and] surround [you],</l>
<l>without despondency quickly bow, think, heart, of him who has one</l>
<l>soft-natured part called Umā, who burned the form of Death,</l>
<l>who wears excellently shining ashes</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
